{
  "stem": "8072.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the people were freezing to dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was, you know, like-- and one of the guys from the three of us wound up in the kitchen, like doing a-- like in a mess hall, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like being a cook or something like that, so we had some extra food, you know, to, to live.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and then we went to work over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the work we did over there was almost like, like, coal mining.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, we had this little-- on these little cars, railroad cars, the small cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember what they did, but we used to dig the-- put some dirt on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Pushed the cars to maybe a half-- maybe half a mile or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Empty it, go back, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember in-- it was in January, the first part of January, I was uncoupling one of these cars.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for some reason, my finger got caught.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- you could still-- you see it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my finger-- tore off my finger, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the skin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was red.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Things like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this, one of the German engineers, whoever, saw it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he took me into their dispensary and he put it a band-aid on, a gauze.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was no thing, just for stopping the bleeding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had that band-aid on for about, I don't know, three days, four days, or five days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that gauze just kind of dried and just kind of grew, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, became-- the blood was-- and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was trying to take it off, you know, myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very painful to take it off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I tried to soak it in cold water.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
